<p>Week 1: Course introduction</p>
<p>Week 2-4: Topic introduction and discussion. Modeling debate.</p>
<p>Week 5: Students choose topic, prepare summaries</p>
<p>Week 6: Small group discussion</p>
<p>Week 7: Poster guidelines explanation and preparation</p>
<p>Week 8-9: Poster presentations</p>
<p>Week 10: argument essay introduction. HW: rough draft</p>
<p>Week 11: peer reading and review, adding counter argument &amp; rebuttal</p>
<p>Week 12: second draft, in text citations, quotations</p>
<p>Week 13: peer review. final draft preparation</p>
<p>Week 14: final draft submission and review</p>
<p>Week 15: final exam/Report</p>
<p>Week 16: final discussion</p></div><div style="margin:20px 3px 3px 3px;padding-top:6px;padding-bottom:3px;padding-left:7px;background-color:lightsteelblue">成績評価の方法</div><div style="margin:10px"><p>[Details will be announced in the class]</p>
